Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.01,0:00:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{=2}Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.38,0:00:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Serika!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.21,0:00:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how excited they are.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.68,0:00:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch your step.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.21,0:00:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.88,0:00:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, shall we be off?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.29,0:00:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.42,0:00:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ayane, what should \Nwe look at first when we get there?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.73,0:00:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good question. I think I'd like \Nto go see the sea turtles.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.62,0:00:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wouldn't you normally start with the fish?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.66,0:00:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko, Hoshino, back me up here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.39,0:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You do have a point.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.76,0:00:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the seahorses then.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.38,0:00:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's also weirdly specific...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.89,0:00:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Does sound like something she'd like.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.78,0:00:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Just look at this place!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we're in the middle of the ocean!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on, there's sharks over there!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.97,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, take it easy, don't trip and fall.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.82,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This aquarium is so big!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We might not get to see everything today.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is it that big?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.20,0:02:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to the fish tanks, \N penguin area, and the dolphin show,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.86,0:02:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they have all sorts of other\N attractions and shops here, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.71,0:02:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do? Should we \Ngo quickly to try to hit everything?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.99,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, no need to get impatient.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we don't get to everything today, we can always come back.
Comment: 10,0:03:04.65,0:03:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ojisan noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.63,0:03:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see all of you are having fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.63,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It keeps opening its mouth!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's how it breathes?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.11,0:03:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I think about it, \Nhow does it breathe underwater?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.39,0:03:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish have this organ that lets them \Nget oxygen from the water, you see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard of gills, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.11,0:03:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Water goes in through their mouths \Nand passes over their gills on the way out.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.78,0:03:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how fish take in oxygen \Nand expel carbon dioxide.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In a sense, they breathe just like we do.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.72,0:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We may look different, but on \Nthe inside, we're all built the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.13,0:03:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are animals like whales \Nthat actually hold their breath while underwater, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.70,0:03:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't really count, \Nsince whales are mammals, not fish.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's everyone all quiet? {TM: check link}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.49,0:04:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I was just a little surprised... {TM: add split alt?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.98,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually said something smart for once.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.06,0:04:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.82,0:04:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're quite the encyclopedia.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.62,0:04:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino knows a lot about fish, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.58,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, shucks, you're making me blush.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.37,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, yeah, I love jellyfish! {TM: alt?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree! The way they glow is so cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.49,0:04:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't shining lights \Non them or anything, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. They glow all on their own!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Curious.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.05,0:04:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't glowing in the middle of the ocean \Njust make it easier to be eaten?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.08,0:04:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, setting aside all the fancy details for now,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.90,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,some of them actually use light to protect themselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.71,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They can even use it to attack, sometimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.94,0:04:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go look at the \Ntropical fish next, pretty please?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they have a great selection!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea. Let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Look at that!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.29,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at those ones! Don't they look just adorable?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.71,0:05:11.24,Alt,,0,0,0,,Delectable!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.67,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But look how plump they are!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're great to look at and even better to eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just insane!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.27,0:05:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You agree with me, right, Ayane?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.97,0:05:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um, I probably wouldn't think to eat them, myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so cute, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But think about it this way, Ayane
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could eat these fish,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd save on food.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,T-True...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Shiroko, not you too!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Nonomi?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.08,0:05:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're cute, of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonomi!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.27,0:05:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also think they look quite tasty!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait, girls. {TM: check leadin}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you all chatting about?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.90,0:06:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Serika, why don't we have \Nthe teacher decide at this point?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea, Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.87,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide? Decide what?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.30,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, Sensei, it's about the tropical fish here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they look cute, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.48,Alt,,0,0,0,,You think they look tasty, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.58,0:06:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Which one is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.40,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.76,0:06:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think all of you look much cuter? {He really tried it}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no. Just... no.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why people make fun of you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.15,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! Let me try that again, please?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It says this fish is called "the Old Man"!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like Hoshino!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.30,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to pick something, \NI'd say she's much more like a jellyfish!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always so laid-back and squishy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Nonomi?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had to pick one...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe a penguin? {TM: check leadin snap}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think they're quite similar!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.92,0:07:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The way they both move is just adorable! {TRUE! --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.82,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It just jumped higher than our heads!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.14,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, does that mean \Nthey'll jump even higher next?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher looks like he's having fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's so happy. He's like a small child!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.71,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look, something's happening!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.37,0:07:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a show!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.26,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a word?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Shiroko?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.96,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to talk in private.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.00,0:08:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Could it be you wanted\N to confess your deep love for me? {Yuri archive real? --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.34,0:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, bummer.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.06,0:08:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, while we were \Nwatching that show, I was thinking.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.44,0:08:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kind of like a dolphin, Shiroko.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.90,0:08:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.98,0:08:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Nonomi and the others were talking \N earlier about what animal I reminded them of.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.69,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was thinking, you're cute, \Nand you're great at sports.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of like a dolphin, you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.71,0:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, totally!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.78,0:08:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? What animal \Ndoes this old man remind you of?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A whale. {Nah, that's Nonomi and her gold card --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.54,0:08:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way. I'm so tiny!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bit of a stretch, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're similar. {TM: Check leadin snap?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how they can swim while sleeping.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.77,0:08:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Or how you can only see a part of them, even up close.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.97,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.90,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How they're always holding their breath.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.35,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you said that you had been taking a nap. {TM: check leadout snap}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.99,0:09:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1450,1900,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}But that was a lie, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.58,0:09:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.10,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can do to help?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.88,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just felt like you've been weighed down \Nby something, something you're not sharing.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help you however I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.57,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like how you did for me once.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a sweet kid, Shiroko.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.91,0:09:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, that's exactly why...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,this old man can't get enough of you! {TM: figure out what to do with this leadin}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, you make me so happy!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.24,0:09:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm lucky to have you in my class.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My, it looks like the two of you \Nare getting along well.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.74,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko was just saying \Nhow much she loves me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane, let's go to the feeding area next.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.38,0:10:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.82,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{If this is TL'd, make last line continuous}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to get one?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, I mean,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.27,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm a little old for this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Comment: 10,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this beauty!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this beauty!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I could even get it back to the room.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you did buy it, where would you put it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the teacher would figure something out. {TM: this and nonomi's line have a possibly weird overlap, for now timed them continuously since I can hear that Nonomi seems to be replying to her. I think it works but ugh.}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.53,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}True. {I don't even think this really needs to be subbed tbh}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's very cute, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.76,0:10:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything you like, Shiroko?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.23,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.68,0:10:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this was cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.97,0:10:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a surprisingly normal choice, \Ncoming from you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.73,0:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But it probably costs a good bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.39,0:11:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, you don't have to worry about that part.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.99,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, we could go for \Nsomething smaller, like a keychain...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, right, Sensei? {TM: check leadin snap}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but, I mean...
Comment: 10,0:11:19.66,0:11:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei? {wiggly wiggly intonation --ik} {Like a jellyfish! --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.66,0:11:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei? {wiggly wiggly intonation --ik} {Like a jellyfish! --ML}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.24,0:11:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy you like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.60,0:11:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now that we're all here, let's take a picture!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.25,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.43,0:11:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm down. {TM: Check kf snap}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.52,0:11:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll take the photo, \Nso the five of you, line up over there. {TM: add split}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.98,0:11:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you not joining us?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I'll be -
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you getting shy about now?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.32,0:11:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're part of this, too, Sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.54,0:11:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just leave you all alone over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.18,0:12:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.48,0:12:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I take the picture for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuka!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancy meeting you here, Sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you again for your help the other day.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.88,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I might take the opportunity \Nto discuss something with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.66,0:12:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems it would be better \Nto save it for another time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.77,0:12:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, we can take the photo for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, please do. {TM: check leadin snap}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here we go.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.29,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Say "cheese"!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.89,0:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the moments \Nthat they deserve to have more of.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.58,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I'm just imagining things.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.20,0:13:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I am now...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.71,0:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,am I doing as good a job as you were, back then?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yume.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.32,0:14:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just my imagination?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that...?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.96,0:15:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks gorgeous in profile.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.05,0:15:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gorgeous normally.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.55,0:15:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! Why don't I send this \Nto the group chat in Momotalk, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.09,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, let's all upload \Nthe photos we each took.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.73,0:15:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.15,0:15:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for Hoshino, she's not here yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.86,0:15:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's off napping somewhere again.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.70,0:15:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you also send over \Nthe photos you took yesterday?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.70,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.83,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, I hadn't sent \Nanything besides the group photo.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.79,0:15:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, where did you take this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a specimen area.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They said we could pick them up, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.67,0:15:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This photo makes it look like you're \Nsaying "I caught this starfish"
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.55,0:15:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like Shiroko would be pretty good at fishing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I might try it out if we get the chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.73,0:15:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go to the actual ocean next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That underwater tunnel was really cool, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.65,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to go diving or something one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. If that happens, \Nwe should all go together again.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, in that case,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.62,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya, everyone, how's it hanging?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.28,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino, you're late!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.54,0:16:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.12,0:16:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just so comfy in my bed, \NI didn't want to move.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's everyone up to?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We were looking at the photos \Nfrom yesterday's aquarium trip.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, nice!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.26,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let this old man join in on the fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not take any pictures, Hoshino?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.72,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All this fancy technology's \Ntoo much for someone my age.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancy technology...?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.60,0:16:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I made sure to take plenty of photos \Nof both Hoshino and everyone else!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Great work, Nonomi!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.49,0:16:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what I'd like to say, but I knew you'd be \Ntoo busy taking photos for everyone else,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so I made sure to take plenty of you as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have many pictures of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika, Ayane.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.29,0:17:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both so thoughtful! I'm touched!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shiroko. Aren't you going to join them?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.02,0:17:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I love you two as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.73,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone, that's it \Nfor today's general meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also be heading home now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.33,0:17:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay Sensei a visit before heading back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.17,0:17:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go home and have a nice snooze.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.14,0:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you this morning?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.35,0:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.43,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't go anywhere, I just overslept, that's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Shiroko?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.61,0:18:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.44,0:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I saw you in town this morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you had the wrong person.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are plenty of girls out there who look just like me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.37,0:18:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably just seeing things \Nbecause you're still tired from yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.05,0:18:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go home and take it easy for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hiding something from -
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Pictures of me?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.43,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'll send them over along with everyone else's.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts, Shiroko.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino, what is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a form.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.82,0:18:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean anything yet, so relax.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.91,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I can relax.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "yet"?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put this...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino? Shiroko?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're, I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.72,0:19:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but just leave us alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I can't do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.69,0:19:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no secrets \Nbetween members of the Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.61,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we're all in this together, as a team!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.87,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But -
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.45,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really not a big deal, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko's such a worrywart.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.59,0:19:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really do appreciate the thought, honest.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hoshino, I'm not done -
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.80,0:20:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.97,0:20:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on, but maybe \Nyou should leave her alone for a little bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hoshino's -
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.90,0:20:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone has something that \Nthey'd rather not talk about.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.74,0:20:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shiroko.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to do this.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the time has finally come.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, this is the point of no return.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.68,0:20:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Once things are set in motion, \Nthere's no going back.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.63,0:22:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Shiroko?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.72,0:22:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've calmed down a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.97,0:22:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, look at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.52,0:22:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.44,0:23:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.65,0:23:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino is hiding something from us.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.91,0:23:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.62,0:23:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's that Hoshino doesn't trust you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.21,0:23:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could let me handle this for now?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.04,0:23:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help Hoshino, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.17,0:23:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so, Sensei...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.30,0:23:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are some things she can't say \N{\i1}because{\i0} she trusts and cares about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.02,0:23:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{=3}Thank you, Sensei.

